        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='11053' id='58' type-v2='text' w='67188' x='6563' y='421'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='26'>CAR INSURANCE CLAIM ANALYTICS</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Insights</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='8526' id='59' is-centered='0' is-scaled='1' param='C:/Users/Abhi/Downloads/car-protection-shield-icon-vector-22266842.jpg' type-v2='bitmap' w='5063' x='1063' y='2421'>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='967' />
            <format attr='margin' value='4' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='88842' id='153' type-v2='text' w='99188' x='438' y='12211'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>1. Claims are concentrated in a smaller group of customers</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Only </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>38.3%</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'> of customers filed a claim, while most customers remained claim-free.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>2. Some customer groups are riskier than others</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Claim costs are not evenly spread across customers. A few segments contribute much more to total claims.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>3. Family size impacts claim risk</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Customers with more children in the household tend to have higher claim amounts.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>4. Parent households show higher exposure</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Families with parents generally experience more claims compared to non-parent households.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>5. Vehicle type matters</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Certain vehicle types, especially </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Panel Trucks</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>, generate higher claim amounts than others.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>6. Young drivers increase risk</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Households with multiple young drivers show higher claim severity and overall risk.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>7. Driving patterns affect claims</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Vehicle age and travel habits have a noticeable impact on claim amounts.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>8. Urban customers generate more claims</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Customers living in urban areas contribute higher claim costs compared to rural customers.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>9. Past claims indicate future risk</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Customers with previous claim history are more likely to generate higher future claims.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>10. Financial factors influence claims</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Income, home value, and vehicle value all play a role in determining claim exposure.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
