    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Recommendations'>
      <style>
        <style-rule element='dash-text'>
          <format attr='text-align' id='dash-text_153' value='left' />
          <format attr='vertical-align' id='dash-text_153' value='top' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size maxheight='950' maxwidth='1600' minheight='950' minwidth='1600' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='6' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='100000' id='5' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#f5f5f5' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
        </zone>
        <zone h='11789' id='3' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99875' x='0' y='105'>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='10' />
            <format attr='background-color' value='#10318c' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='11053' id='58' type-v2='text' w='67188' x='6563' y='421'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='26'>CAR INSURANCE CLAIM ANALYTICS</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Recommendation</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='8526' id='59' is-centered='0' is-scaled='1' param='C:/Users/Abhi/Downloads/car-protection-shield-icon-vector-22266842.jpg' type-v2='bitmap' w='5063' x='1063' y='2421'>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='967' />
            <format attr='margin' value='4' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='88842' id='153' type-v2='text' w='99188' x='438' y='12211'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>1. Price policies based on risk</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Charge higher premiums for high-risk vehicles and customer segments.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>2. Focus on high-risk households</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Pay closer attention to households with multiple children and young drivers.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>3. Reward safe customers</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Offer discounts and benefits to customers who remain claim-free.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>4. Use claim history in decision-making</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Previous claims should be considered when renewing policies or setting premiums.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>5. Improve urban risk management</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Introduce safety programs and targeted strategies for urban customers.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>6. Monitor high-risk vehicles</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Keep a closer watch on vehicle types that generate larger claim amounts.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>7. Create targeted insurance plans</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Design products specifically for high-risk and high-exposure customer groups.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='16'>FINAL CONCLUSION</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Insurance risk is influenced by customer behavior, household characteristics, vehicle type, driving patterns, location, and financial factors. By focusing on high-risk segments and rewarding low-risk customers, insurers can reduce claim costs, improve profitability, and make better business decisions.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
        <devicelayout auto-generated='true' name='Phone'>
          <size maxheight='700' minheight='700' sizing-mode='vscroll' />
          <zones>
            <zone h='100000' id='161' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
              <zone h='98316' id='160' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='99000' x='500' y='842'>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='11053' id='58' type-v2='text' w='67188' x='6563' y='421'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='26'>CAR INSURANCE CLAIM ANALYTICS</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Recommendation</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone fixed-size='73' h='8526' id='59' is-centered='0' is-fixed='true' is-scaled='1' param='C:/Users/Abhi/Downloads/car-protection-shield-icon-vector-22266842.jpg' type-v2='bitmap' w='5063' x='1063' y='2421'>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <_.fcp.DashboardRoundedCorners.true...format attr='corner-radius' value='967' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='88842' id='153' type-v2='text' w='99188' x='438' y='12211'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>1. Price policies based on risk</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Charge higher premiums for high-risk vehicles and customer segments.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>2. Focus on high-risk households</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Pay closer attention to households with multiple children and young drivers.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>3. Reward safe customers</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Offer discounts and benefits to customers who remain claim-free.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>4. Use claim history in decision-making</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Previous claims should be considered when renewing policies or setting premiums.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>5. Improve urban risk management</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Introduce safety programs and targeted strategies for urban customers.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>6. Monitor high-risk vehicles</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Keep a closer watch on vehicle types that generate larger claim amounts.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>7. Create targeted insurance plans</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Design products specifically for high-risk and high-exposure customer groups.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='16'>FINAL CONCLUSION</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='14'>Insurance risk is influenced by customer behavior, household characteristics, vehicle type, driving patterns, location, and financial factors. By focusing on high-risk segments and rewarding low-risk customers, insurers can reduce claim costs, improve profitability, and make better business decisions.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zones>
        </devicelayout>
      </devicelayouts>
